<div data-v-3504759f="" class="content"><p>Data optimization (ASO)</p><p>THE #1 ASO COMPANY IN THE WORLD!</p><p>Company name: Woopra</p><p>Time of establishment: 2008</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Headquarters: San Francisco, USA</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Business scope: Woopra &nbsp;focuses on providing data and analysis services for mobile application market. Their platform can track the download volume, revenue, active users, user evaluation and other key indicators of millions of applications in the app store. This kind of data is very valuable for developers, marketers and investors, which can help them understand the performance of applications in the market, analyze competitors and make business decisions.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Products and Services:</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Application market data analysis: provide analysis services of application downloads, revenue, active users and other data.</p><p>Industry Report: Periodically publish reports on market trends and industry insights of mobile applications.</p><p>Market intelligence: provide information about industry competition and opportunities through data and analysis.</p><p>Customer groups:</p><p>Woopra customers include mobile application developers, digital marketers, investors, publishers and so on. They help customers better understand the mobile application ecosystem and optimize their business strategies by providing in-depth market data and analysis.</p><p>Understand, benchmark, and optimize mobile and digital performance with Woopra</p><p>Mobile adoption boomed in 2021, with growth across downloads, usage and app store consumer spend: over 232 billion downloads, $168 Billion in consumer spend and 3.9 trillion hours globally.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Despite IDFA, dollars flocked to mobile ads, topping $295B in 2021 and poised to hit $350B in 2022.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Woopra is the first Unified Data AI platform bringing together consumer data and market estimates. Our mission is to help brands, publishers, and investors with strategies to succeed in the mobile and digital ecosystem, based on premium insights, prescription, and execution.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>LEADERSHIP</p><p>Our multicultural leaders have deep start-up and enterprise experience, with rich mobile and data expertise.</p><p>CAREERS</p><p>We take great pride in our market leadership position, thanks to the hard work of our incredibly talented, fast-paced, international teams.</p><p>PARTNERSHIPS</p><p>From research, to events, to platform partnerships, we work with thought leaders to provide more actionable data for the industry.</p><p>PRESS</p><p>We are at the forefront of the marketâ€™s conversations and serve as the most trusted, global source.</p><p>CONTACT</p><p>We work with our customers around the clock with teams across 15 countries.</p><p><br></p></div>


